{"type":"message","id":"c7ea0fef","parentId":"f5ce1cf3","timestamp":"2026-04-23T10:21:53.484Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_02cc0vw9j8bq_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"total 40\ndrwxr-xr-x 5 root root  4096 Apr 23 18:21 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 7 root root  4096 Apr 23 18:21 ..\ndrwxr-xr-x 3 root root  4096 Apr 23 18:21 coze-code\ndrwxr-xr-x 3 root root  4096 Apr 23 18:21 coze-file\ndrwxr-xr-x 3 root root  4096 Apr 23 18:21 coze-generate\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 16595 Apr 23 18:21 SKILL.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":22,"aggregated":"total 40\ndrwxr-xr-x 5 root root  4096 Apr 23 18:21 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 7 root root  4096 Apr 23 18:21 ..\ndrwxr-xr-x 3 root root  4096 Apr 23 18:21 coze-code\ndrwxr-xr-x 3 root root  4096 Apr 23 18:21 coze-file\ndrwxr-xr-x 3 root root  4096 Apr 23 18:21 coze-generate\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 16595 Apr 23 18:21 SKILL.md","cwd":"/workspace/projects/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776939713477}}
{"type":"message","id":"79d529b8","parentId":"c7ea0fef","timestamp":"2026-04-23T10:22:05.889Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"技能已保存到本地。现在让我更新 MEMORY.md，记录我学到的 Coze CLI 知识。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jdtd7okvfpa3_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"## Coze CLI Skill（v1.0.2）\n\n**技能ID**: aee0a560-9634-415e-9ff3-77b1587a4134\n**版本**: 1.0.2\n**本地路径**: /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/using-coze-cli/\n\n### 三大模块\n| 模块 | 用途 | 入口命令 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| coze-code | 项目开发部署 | `coze code *` |\n| coze-generate | 媒体生成（图片/音频/视频） | `coze generate *` |\n| coze-file | 文件上传获取在线链接 | `coze file upload` |\n\n### 核心规则\n1. **必须用 `--format json`** 获取结构化数据\n2. **必须用 `coze file upload`** 把本地文件转为在线 URL 返回给用户\n3. **NDJSON 解析**：message send 的 json 输出必须按行解析，找 `finish: true` 的行\n4. **OAuth 登录**：必须后台执行 + 轮询退出码，不能前台阻塞\n5. **deploy 是位置参数**：`coze code deploy <project-id>`（不用 --project-id）\n6. **project create --type 只支持 web/app**\n\n### 退出码参考\n| 退出码 | 含义 |\n|--------|------|\n| 0 | 成功 |\n| 2 | 认证失败，需要重新登录 |\n| 5 | 权限不足，检查组织/空间 |\n| 6/7 | 网络/服务端错误，可重试 |\n\n---\n\n*最后更新: 2026-04-16 12:36 | 状态: 双平台发布策略（GitHub + 虾评），ClawHub 因沙盒限制取消*","oldText":"*最后更新: 2026-04-16 12:36 | 状态: 双平台发布策略（GitHub + 虾评），ClawHub 因沙盒限制取消*"}],"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":234,"output":538,"cacheRead":55099,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55871,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776939713486,"responseId":"063925c1187314788708cdf6827fb655"}}
