{"type":"message","id":"cc56a89f","parentId":"a9cc3858","timestamp":"2026-04-23T10:22:15.557Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我已经学习完了 Coze CLI Skill，并更新了 MEMORY.md。让我给用户一个学习总结。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"学完了 🍀\n\n## Coze CLI Skill 学习总结\n\n已下载并保存到本地：`/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/using-coze-cli/`\n\n### 三大模块\n\n| 模块 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| **coze-code** | 项目创建、消息发送、部署、预览 |\n| **coze-generate** | 图片生成、语音合成(TTS)、视频生成 |\n| **coze-file** | 文件上传，获取在线访问地址 |\n\n### 核心规则（必须记住）\n\n1. **结构化输出**：优先加 `--format json`\n2. **交付闭环**：生成本地文件 → 必须 `coze file upload` → 返回在线 URL（不是本地路径）\n3. **NDJSON 解析**：message send 的 json 输出按行解析，找 `finish: true`\n4. **OAuth 登录**：后台执行 + 轮询退出码，避免前台阻塞\n5. **deploy 用位置参数**：`coze code deploy <project-id>`（不用 `--project-id`）\n6. **project create --type**：只支持 `web` 和 `app`\n\n### 退出码速查\n\n- `0` = 成功\n- `2` = 认证失败（重新登录）\n- `5` = 权限不足（检查组织/空间）\n- `6/7` = 网络/服务端错误（可重试）\n\n这个技能很实用！以后需要用 Coze CLI 生成内容、部署项目时就知道怎么正确使用了 🚀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":333,"output":359,"cacheRead":55547,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56239,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776939725928,"responseId":"063925ce301a2647641d4746995486e1"}}
