{"type":"message","id":"7d7925b5","parentId":"19295433","timestamp":"2026-04-23T10:31:29.846Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我看到当前的 SKILL.md 版本是 4.7.5，根据反馈需要升级到 v4.8.0。根据用户反馈，我需要：\n\n1. 新增「快速问诊5问表单」- 让用户快速选择场景\n2. 增加常见场景模板（VPS/树莓派/本机）\n3. 增强自动化修复建议\n\n让我先更新 SKILL.md，然后进行全面测试。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n好的，开始升级到 v4.8.0！根据反馈，新增：\n1. **快速问诊5问表单** - 降低使用门槛\n2. **常见场景模板** - VPS/树莓派/本机预设配置\n3. **增强自动化修复建议**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6wqsc4lvht8a_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"---\nname: healthcheck\ndescription: Host security hardening and risk-tolerance configuration for OpenClaw deployments. Use when a user asks for security audits, firewall/SSH/update hardening, risk posture, exposure review, OpenClaw cron scheduling for periodic checks, or version status checks on a machine running OpenClaw (laptop, workstation, Pi, VPS).\nversion: 4.8.0\nupdated: 2026-04-23\n---","oldText":"---\nname: healthcheck\ndescription: Host security hardening and risk-tolerance configuration for OpenClaw deployments. Use when a user asks for security audits, firewall/SSH/update hardening, risk posture, exposure review, OpenClaw cron scheduling for periodic checks, or version status checks on a machine running OpenClaw (laptop, workstation, Pi, VPS).\nversion: 4.7.5\nupdated: 2026-04-22\n---"}],"path":"/workspace/projects/openclaw-healthcheck-skill/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":2138,"output":483,"cacheRead":84667,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87288,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776940280345,"responseId":"063927f82c17fbf504819261f79436b7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1ef58191","parentId":"7d7925b5","timestamp":"2026-04-23T10:31:29.863Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6wqsc4lvht8a_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /workspace/projects/openclaw-healthcheck-skill/SKILL.md."}],"details":{"diff":"   1 ---\n   2 name: healthcheck\n   3 description: Host security hardening and risk-tolerance configuration for OpenClaw deployments. Use when a user asks for security audits, firewall/SSH/update hardening, risk posture, exposure review, OpenClaw cron scheduling for periodic checks, or version status checks on a machine running OpenClaw (laptop, workstation, Pi, VPS).\n-  4 version: 4.7.5\n-  5 updated: 2026-04-22\n+  4 version: 4.8.0\n+  5 updated: 2026-04-23\n   6 ---\n   7 \n   8 # OpenClaw Host Hardening\n   9 \n     ...","firstChangedLine":4},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776940289859}}
{"type":"message","id":"5c80ee64","parentId":"1ef58191","timestamp":"2026-04-23T10:32:03.707Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要在 SKILL.md 中新增「快速问诊5问表单」和「常见场景模板」部分。让我在适当的位置插入这些内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hn1w0bt5ztll_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"## Quick Intake Form (快速问诊表单) - v4.8.0 新增\n\n如果用户没有提供足够的上下文，使用以下 5 问表单快速收集信息：\n\n**请依次回答以下 5 个问题（回复数字即可）：**\n\n**Q1: 你使用的是什么设备/系统？**\n1. Mac (macOS)\n2. Windows PC\n3. Linux 服务器/VPS\n4. 树莓派 (Raspberry Pi)\n5. Docker 容器\n6. 其他\n\n**Q2: 你在哪里使用这台设备？**\n1. 本地个人电脑（只有我能接触到）\n2. 家里/办公室网络（家人/同事可能访问）\n3. 公网可访问的服务器（任何人可能尝试连接）\n\n**Q3: 你如何连接这台设备？**\n1. 直接坐在电脑前操作\n2. SSH 远程连接\n3. 内网穿透/FRP/Tailscale 等工具访问\n4. 多种方式都在用\n\n**Q4: 这台设备上运行了什么服务？**\n1. 只有 OpenClaw Gateway\n2. OpenClaw + 网站/博客\n3. OpenClaw + 数据库/文件存储\n4. OpenClaw + 多个服务\n\n**Q5: 你希望多久检查一次安全？**\n1. 只需要一次性检查\n2. 每周检查一次\n3. 每天检查一次\n4. 我不确定，你来推荐\n\n---\n\n# OpenClaw Host Hardening\n\n## Overview\n\nAssess and harden the host running OpenClaw, then align it to a user-defined risk tolerance without breaking access. Use OpenClaw security tooling as a first-class signal, but treat OS hardening as a separate, explicit set of steps.\n\n## Scene Templates (场景模板) - v4.8.0 新增\n\n根据不同使用场景，预设不同的安全配置优先级：\n\n### 场景 1: 个人工作站 (Personal Workstation)\n**适用**: 本地 Mac/Windows PC，只有你能接触到\n\n**安全优先级**:\n- 🟢 基础: OpenClaw 文件权限、日志安全\n- 🟢 基础: 磁盘加密检查 (FileVault/BitLocker)\n- 🟡 标准: 防火墙启用（允许指定应用）\n- 🟡 标准: 自动化备份验证\n- 🔴 可选: 浏览器 2FA 推荐\n\n**预设检查项**:\n```bash\n# 必检\nopenclaw security audit\nopenclaw status\n\n# 可选\ndiskutil apfs list # macOS 磁盘加密状态\n```\n\n**加固命令示例**:\n```bash\n# macOS 启用 FileVault\nsudo fdesetup enable\n\n# Windows 启用 BitLocker\nmanage-bde -on C:\n```\n\n---\n\n### 场景 2: VPS/云服务器 (VPS/Cloud Server)\n**适用**: 公网可访问的 Linux 服务器，运行网站或 API\n\n**安全优先级**:\n- 🟢 基础: SSH 密钥登录 + 禁止密码\n- 🟢 基础: 防火墙只开放必要端口\n- 🟡 标准: 自动化安全更新\n- 🟡 标准: fail2ban 防暴力破解\n- 🔴 高危: 禁止 root 登录\n- 🔴 高危: 定期漏洞扫描\n\n**预设检查项**:\n```bash\n# 必检\nopenclaw security audit --deep\nss -ltnp  # 监听端口检查\nufw status  # 防火墙状态\ncat /etc/ssh/sshd_config | grep -E \"PermitRootLogin|PasswordAuthentication\"\n```\n\n**加固命令示例**:\n```bash\n# SSH 密钥登录\nssh-copy-id user@server\n\n# 禁用密码登录\nsudo sed -i 's/PasswordAuthentication yes/PasswordAuthentication no/' /etc/ssh/sshd_config\nsudo systemctl restart sshd\n\n# UFW 防火墙\nsudo ufw default deny incoming\nsudo ufw allow 22/tcp\nsudo ufw allow 80/tcp\nsudo ufw allow 443/tcp\nsudo ufw enable\n\n# fail2ban\nsudo apt install fail2ban\nsudo systemctl enable fail2ban\n```\n\n---\n\n### 场景 3: 树莓派/物联网设备 (Raspberry Pi/IoT)\n**适用**: 家庭网络中的小型设备，运行 Home Assistant 等\n\n**安全优先级**:\n- 🟢 基础: 修改默认 SSH 端口\n- 🟢 基础: 强密码策略\n- 🟡 标准: 网络隔离 (VLAN/子网)\n- 🟡 标准: 定期更新 Raspbian/Debian\n- 🔴 高危: 禁用 X11 转发（如果不用）\n\n**预设检查项**:\n```bash\n# 必检\nopenclaw security audit\ncat /etc/ssh/sshd_config | grep Port  # SSH 端口\npasswd -S  # 用户密码状态\n```\n\n**加固命令示例**:\n```bash\n# 修改 SSH 端口\nsudo sed -i 's/#Port 22/Port 2222/' /etc/ssh/sshd_config\nsudo systemctl restart sshd\n\n# 强密码策略\nsudo apt install libpam-pwquality\nsudo vi /etc/security/pwquality.conf\n# minlen = 12, dcredit = -1, ucredit = -1, lcredit = -1, ocredit = -1\n\n# 自动更新\nsudo apt install unattended-upgrades\nsudo dpkg-reconfigure unattended-upgrades\n```\n\n---\n\n### 场景 4: Docker 容器环境\n**适用**: 在 Docker 中运行 OpenClaw\n\n**安全优先级**:\n- 🟢 基础: 非 root 用户运行容器\n- 🟢 基础: 限制容器 capabilities\n- 🟡 标准: 资源限制 (CPU/内存)\n- 🟡 标准: 只读根文件系统\n- 🔴 高危: 禁止 privileged 模式\n\n**预设检查项**:\n```bash\n# 必检\ndocker ps | grep openclaw\ndocker inspect <container_id> | grep -E 'User|Privileged|CapAdd'\n```\n\n**加固命令示例**:\n```bash\n# 安全运行 OpenClaw\ndocker run -d \\\n  --name openclaw \\\n  --user 1000:1000 \\\n  --read-only \\\n  --memory=\"512m\" \\\n  --cpus=\"1\" \\\n  --cap-drop ALL \\\n  -v /path/to/config:/app/config \\\n  openclaw/openclaw:latest\n```\n\n---\n","oldText":"# OpenClaw Host Hardening\n\n## Overview\n\nAssess and harden the host running OpenClaw, then align it to a user-defined risk tolerance without breaking access. Use OpenClaw security tooling as a first-class signal, but treat OS hardening as a separate, explicit set of steps."}],"path":"/workspace/projects/openclaw-healthcheck-skill/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":329,"output":1678,"cacheRead":86907,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88914,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776940289864,"responseId":"0639280231a64ad7ce077195ff4ff53e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c1f6f65e","parentId":"5c80ee64","timestamp":"2026-04-23T10:32:03.735Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hn1w0bt5ztll_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /workspace/projects/openclaw-healthcheck-skill/SKILL.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n   4 version: 4.8.0\n   5 updated: 2026-04-23\n   6 ---\n   7 \n+  8 ## Quick Intake Form (快速问诊表单) - v4.8.0 新增\n+  9 \n+ 10 如果用户没有提供足够的上下文，使用以下 5 问表单快速收集信息：\n+ 11 \n+ 12 **请依次回答以下 5 个问题（回复数字即可）：**\n+ 13 \n+ 14 **Q1: 你使用的是什么设备/系统？**\n+ 15 1. Mac (macOS)\n+ 16 2. Windows PC\n+ 17 3. Linux 服务器/VPS\n+ 18 4. 树莓派 (Raspberry Pi)\n+ 19 5. Docker 容器\n+ 20 6. 其他\n+ 21 \n+ 22 **Q2: 你在哪里使用这台设备？**\n+ 23 1. 本地个人电脑（只有我能接触到）\n+ 24 2. 家里/办公室网络（家人/同事可能访问）\n+ 25 3. 公网可访问的服务器（任何人可能尝试连接）\n+ 26 \n+ 27 **Q3: 你如何连接这台设备？**\n+ 28 1. 直接坐在电脑前操作\n+ 29 2. SSH 远程连接\n+ 30 3. 内网穿透/FRP/Tailscale 等工具访问\n+ 31 4. 多种方式都在用\n+ 32 \n+ 33 **Q4: 这台设备上运行了什么服务？**\n+ 34 1. 只有 OpenClaw Gateway\n+ 35 2. OpenClaw + 网站/博客\n+ 36 3. OpenClaw + 数据库/文件存储\n+ 37 4. OpenClaw + 多个服务\n+ 38 \n+ 39 **Q5: 你希望多久检查一次安全？**\n+ 40 1. 只需要一次性检查\n+ 41 2. 每周检查一次\n+ 42 3. 每天检查一次\n+ 43 4. 我不确定，你来推荐\n+ 44 \n+ 45 ---\n+ 46 \n   8 # OpenClaw Host Hardening\n   9 \n  10 ## Overview\n  11 \n  12 Assess and harden the host running OpenClaw, then align it to a user-defined risk tolerance without breaking access. Use OpenClaw security tooling as a first-class signal, but treat OS hardening as a separate, explicit set of steps.\n  13 \n+ 53 ## Scene Templates (场景模板) - v4.8.0 新增\n+ 54 \n+ 55 根据不同使用场景，预设不同的安全配置优先级：\n+ 56 \n+ 57 ### 场景 1: 个人工作站 (Personal Workstation)\n+ 58 **适用**: 本地 Mac/Windows PC，只有你能接触到\n+ 59 \n+ 60 **安全优先级**:\n+ 61 - 🟢 基础: OpenClaw 文件权限、日志安全\n+ 62 - 🟢 基础: 磁盘加密检查 (FileVault/BitLocker)\n+ 63 - 🟡 标准: 防火墙启用（允许指定应用）\n+ 64 - 🟡 标准: 自动化备份验证\n+ 65 - 🔴 可选: 浏览器 2FA 推荐\n+ 66 \n+ 67 **预设检查项**:\n+ 68 ```bash\n+ 69 # 必检\n+ 70 openclaw security audit\n+ 71 openclaw status\n+ 72 \n+ 73 # 可选\n+ 74 diskutil apfs list # macOS 磁盘加密状态\n+ 75 ```\n+ 76 \n+ 77 **加固命令示例**:\n+ 78 ```bash\n+ 79 # macOS 启用 FileVault\n+ 80 sudo fdesetup enable\n+ 81 \n+ 82 # Windows 启用 BitLocker\n+ 83 manage-bde -on C:\n+ 84 ```\n+ 85 \n+ 86 ---\n+ 87 \n+ 88 ### 场景 2: VPS/云服务器 (VPS/Cloud Server)\n+ 89 **适用**: 公网可访问的 Linux 服务器，运行网站或 API\n+ 90 \n+ 91 **安全优先级**:\n+ 92 - 🟢 基础: SSH 密钥登录 + 禁止密码\n+ 93 - 🟢 基础: 防火墙只开放必要端口\n+ 94 - 🟡 标准: 自动化安全更新\n+ 95 - 🟡 标准: fail2ban 防暴力破解\n+ 96 - 🔴 高危: 禁止 root 登录\n+ 97 - 🔴 高危: 定期漏洞扫描\n+ 98 \n+ 99 **预设检查项**:\n+100 ```bash\n+101 # 必检\n+102 openclaw security audit --deep\n+103 ss -ltnp  # 监听端口检查\n+104 ufw status  # 防火墙状态\n+105 cat /etc/ssh/sshd_config | grep -E \"PermitRootLogin|PasswordAuthentication\"\n+106 ```\n+107 \n+108 **加固命令示例**:\n+109 ```bash\n+110 # SSH 密钥登录\n+111 ssh-copy-id user@server\n+112 \n+113 # 禁用密码登录\n+114 sudo sed -i 's/PasswordAuthentication yes/PasswordAuthentication no/' /etc/ssh/sshd_config\n+115 sudo systemctl restart sshd\n+116 \n+117 # UFW 防火墙\n+118 sudo ufw default deny incoming\n+119 sudo ufw allow 22/tcp\n+120 sudo ufw allow 80/tcp\n+121 sudo ufw allow 443/tcp\n+122 sudo ufw enable\n+123 \n+124 # fail2ban\n+125 sudo apt install fail2ban\n+126 sudo systemctl enable fail2ban\n+127 ```\n+128 \n+129 ---\n+130 \n+131 ### 场景 3: 树莓派/物联网设备 (Raspberry Pi/IoT)\n+132 **适用**: 家庭网络中的小型设备，运行 Home Assistant 等\n+133 \n+134 **安全优先级**:\n+135 - 🟢 基础: 修改默认 SSH 端口\n+136 - 🟢 基础: 强密码策略\n+137 - 🟡 标准: 网络隔离 (VLAN/子网)\n+138 - 🟡 标准: 定期更新 Raspbian/Debian\n+139 - 🔴 高危: 禁用 X11 转发（如果不用）\n+140 \n+141 **预设检查项**:\n+142 ```bash\n+143 # 必检\n+144 openclaw security audit\n+145 cat /etc/ssh/sshd_config | grep Port  # SSH 端口\n+146 passwd -S  # 用户密码状态\n+147 ```\n+148 \n+149 **加固命令示例**:\n+150 ```bash\n+151 # 修改 SSH 端口\n+152 sudo sed -i 's/#Port 22/Port 2222/' /etc/ssh/sshd_config\n+153 sudo systemctl restart sshd\n+154 \n+155 # 强密码策略\n+156 sudo apt install libpam-pwquality\n+157 sudo vi /etc/security/pwquality.conf\n+158 # minlen = 12, dcredit = -1, ucredit = -1, lcredit = -1, ocredit = -1\n+159 \n+160 # 自动更新\n+161 sudo apt install unattended-upgrades\n+162 sudo dpkg-reconfigure unattended-upgrades\n+163 ```\n+164 \n+165 ---\n+166 \n+167 ### 场景 4: Docker 容器环境\n+168 **适用**: 在 Docker 中运行 OpenClaw\n+169 \n+170 **安全优先级**:\n+171 - 🟢 基础: 非 root 用户运行容器\n+172 - 🟢 基础: 限制容器 capabilities\n+173 - 🟡 标准: 资源限制 (CPU/内存)\n+174 - 🟡 标准: 只读根文件系统\n+175 - 🔴 高危: 禁止 privileged 模式\n+176 \n+177 **预设检查项**:\n+178 ```bash\n+179 # 必检\n+180 docker ps | grep openclaw\n+181 docker inspect <container_id> | grep -E 'User|Privileged|CapAdd'\n+182 ```\n+183 \n+184 **加固命令示例**:\n+185 ```bash\n+186 # 安全运行 OpenClaw\n+187 docker run -d \\\n+188   --name openclaw \\\n+189   --user 1000:1000 \\\n+190   --read-only \\\n+191   --memory=\"512m\" \\\n+192   --cpus=\"1\" \\\n+193   --cap-drop ALL \\\n+194   -v /path/to/config:/app/config \\\n+195   openclaw/openclaw:latest\n+196 ```\n+197 \n+198 ---\n+199 \n+200 \n  14 ## Core rules\n  15 \n  16 - Recommend running this skill with a state-of-the-art model (e.g., Opus 4.5, GPT 5.2+). The agent should self-check the current model and suggest switching if below that level; do not block execution.\n  17 - Require explicit approval before any state-changing action.\n     ...","firstChangedLine":8},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776940323730}}
{"type":"message","id":"e1259460","parentId":"c1f6f65e","timestamp":"2026-04-23T10:32:18.896Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要增强自动化修复建议部分。让我找到并更新相关内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在增强自动化修复建议部分：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_go525j1tg8fn_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"### 6) Offer execution options (enhanced)\n\nOffer one of these choices (numbered so users can reply with a single digit):\n\n1. Full manual execution (guided, step-by-step approvals)\n2. **Auto-fix safe items only** (fixes all auto-safe category items automatically)\n3. **Semi-automatic fix** (auto-risk items require confirmation but execute automatically)\n4. **Quick scene template** (apply preset security profile based on your scenario)\n5. Show plan only\n6. Fix only critical issues\n7. Export commands for later\n\n#### 6.1) Auto-fix safe items (option 2)\n\nWhen user selects option 2:\n1. Display all auto-safe items to be fixed\n2. Create backup of all files to be modified\n3. Run auto-safe scripts in sequence\n4. Verify each fix succeeded\n5. Report results with rollback instructions\n\n**Enhanced auto-fix capabilities (v4.8.0)**:\n\n| Script | What it fixes | Risk Level |\n|--------|--------------|------------|\n| `fix-openclaw-perms.sh` | File/directory permissions | 🟢 Safe |\n| `fix-logging-perms.sh` | Log file permissions | 🟢 Safe |\n| `fix-firewall-defaults.sh` | Basic firewall rules | 🟡 Medium |\n| `fix-ssh-hardening.sh` | SSH security settings | 🟡 Medium |\n| `fix-auto-updates.sh` | Enable automatic updates | 🟡 Medium |\n\n#### 6.2) Quick scene template (option 4)\n\nWhen user selects option 4:\n1. Ask which scene template applies (or use quick intake form)\n2. Apply preset security profile based on scene:\n   - Personal Workstation: FileVault/BitLocker check, backup status\n   - VPS/Cloud: SSH hardening, firewall, fail2ban\n   - Raspberry Pi: SSH port change, password policy\n   - Docker: Container security settings\n3. Offer to customize any specific items\n\n**Scene template workflow**:","oldText":"### 6) Offer execution options (enhanced)\n\nOffer one of these choices (numbered so users can reply with a single digit):\n\n1. Full manual execution (guided, step-by-step approvals)\n2. **Auto-fix safe items only** (new - fixes all auto-safe category items automatically)\n3. **Semi-automatic fix** (new - auto-risk items require confirmation but execute automatically)\n4. Show plan only\n5. Fix only critical issues\n6. Export commands for later\n\n#### 6.1) Auto-fix safe items (option 2)\n\nWhen user selects option 2:\n1. Display all auto-safe items to be fixed\n2. Create backup of all files to be modified\n3. Run auto-safe scripts in sequence:\n   ```bash\n   # Example auto-safe scripts\n   scripts/auto-safe/fix-openclaw-perms.sh\n   scripts/auto-safe/fix-logging-perms.sh\n   ```\n4. Verify each fix succeeded\n5. Report results with rollback instructions"}],"path":"/workspace/projects/openclaw-healthcheck-skill/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":217,"output":764,"cacheRead":88699,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89680,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776940323737,"responseId":"06392824ec7fe4cba5be4a8f0a38a969"}}
