`fix-firewall-defaults.sh` | Basic firewall rules | 🟡 Medium |\n+369 | `fix-ssh-hardening.sh` | SSH security settings | 🟡 Medium |\n+370 | `fix-auto-updates.sh` | Enable automatic updates | 🟡 Medium |\n+371 \n+372 #### 6.2) Quick scene template (option 4)\n+373 \n+374 When user selects option 4:\n+375 1. Ask which scene template applies (or use quick intake form)\n+376 2. Apply preset security profile based on scene:\n+377    - Personal Workstation: FileVault/BitLocker check, backup status\n+378    - VPS/Cloud: SSH hardening, firewall, fail2ban\n+379    - Raspberry Pi: SSH port change, password policy\n+380    - Docker: Container security settings\n+381 3. Offer to customize any specific items\n+382 \n+383 **Scene template workflow**:\n+384 \n 366 Auto-safe scripts characteristics:\n 367 - Always create backup before modification\n 368 - Use non-destructive operations\n 369 - Provide rollback instructions in output\n     ...","firstChangedLine":346},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776940338908}}
{"type":"message","id":"09622570","parentId":"e82ef305","timestamp":"2026-04-23T10:32:22.470Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要创建新的自动修复脚本，然后进行测试验证。让我先创建 `fix-firewall-defaults.sh`、`fix-ssh-hardening.sh` 和 `fix-auto-updates.sh` 这三个新的自动修复脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在创建新的自动修复脚本：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_89ey1o4s2zkc_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /workspace/projects/openclaw-healthcheck-skill/scripts/auto-safe"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":104,"output":143,"cacheRead":89595,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89842,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776940338913,"responseId":"06392833fefc827af612825448a3b1f3"}}
